Editor's note: The Beijing Winter Olympics is conducted under the concept of "Science and Technology Winter Olympics." The "double-Olympics" city has put Chinese tech, including smart beds, 5G connection, AI tools, green energy, etc., on display at the Winter Games. The latest episode of "Thought Bubble" gives you another closer look at China's ingenuity in Beijing 2022. Episode VIII: Smart tech preventing COVID-19 at the Games Episode VII: Cool tech in venues for 2022 Beijing Winter Olympics Editor: Yuan Xin Senior producer: Wei Wei Managing director: Mei Yan (To submit cartoons and share story ideas or feedback on our cartoon page, please contact us at cartoon_opinions@cgtn.com) 